songs.title: Murder Dull Mind
songs.lyrics:
I know what I have and we found
We got to lose
We got to lose
We got to lose

You get up, find yourself
What’s that you know?
What’s that you know?
What’s that you know?

Murder mind, dull mind
I would do down, do down

What’s that you know?
What’s that you know?
What’s that you know?

What’s that you know?
What’s that you know?
What’s that you know?

Turn in my own
Turn into yourself
You notice yourself
You notice yourself
You notice yourself
